---
title: Blog
description: Blog of Dave Clark, a full-stack web developer. Guides and tutorials on various topics such as Ruby, Python, JavaScript and Chef
menu: blog
pageable: true
per_page: 200
---
%section{:id => 'content', :class => 'blog'}
  - page_articles.each_with_index do |article, i|
    .blog-entry
      %aside
        .date
          .month= article.date.strftime('%^b')
          .day= article.date.strftime('%e')
      %article
        %h2= link_to article.title, article
        - if article.summary?
          ~ article.summary
          .read-more
            = link_to 'Continue reading &rsaquo;', article
        - else
          ~ article.body
